text: Oberwinterthur is a district in the city of Winterthur in Switzerland. It is District number 2. The district has these quarters: Talacker, Guggenbühl, Zinzikon, Reutlingen, Stadel, Grüze, Hegmatten and Hegi. Until 1922, it was a municipality on its own. Then it became part of Winterthur.
